{
  "stem": "1419.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took 10 Jews out from, from-- a little bit older Jews from Nowy Sacz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to watch him-- how they hanged them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they hanged 10 Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And our job was to cut them down and to drag 'em to the forest and to bury 'em.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one guy between those people was a guy who used to be a-- like a, a cleaner for the-- for the-- for the Rosenbaum.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He brought him back from Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was like his-- what they call that-- handyman around him, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know what-- what I mean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know why he wanna hang this particularly guy too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wanna hang him between the 10 Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the guy-- they was thin, thin strings, and he was just, just falling, and they were-- what they call it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They ripped the-- you know, they falling down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't hold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The, the strings were too thin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he begged them, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Shoot me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they hanged him so many times, about three, four times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's what I was on a trial, and that's what we testified.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to pull these other people-- most of them were still alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were not hanged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were just [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We used to carry them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were-- we were just happy that we were not them, because, you know, we were-- we were-- we were sure they were gonna kill us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had to bury him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[SIGHS] That was-- that was my incident in Rabka what I had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's how I testified in, in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And not only me, all the people which came back to testify, which they-- we went through that particularly incident, that experience we went through.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
